Introduction

Park Ji Sung, also known as Jisung, is a South Korean singer and rapper under SM Entertainment. He is a member of the boy group NCT.

On August 25, 2016, Jisung debuted as a member of the sub-unit NCT Dream. He was born in Seoul on February 5, 2002, making him the maknae of the group.
